.TH "INSTAGRAM-ARCHIVER" "1" "Apr 26, 2026" "0.4.0" "instagram-archiver"
.SH NAME
instagram-archiver \- instagram-archiver v0.4.0
.SH COMMANDS
.SS instagram\-archiver
.sp
Archive a profile (USERNAME) or your saved posts (\-\-saved).
.sp
Pass exactly one of: a USERNAME positional argument, or \fB\-\-saved\fP/\fB\-s\fP\&.
.sp
Usage
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
instagram\-archiver [OPTIONS] [USERNAME]
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Options
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-o, \-\-output\-dir <output_dir>
Output directory. Defaults to the username (profile mode) or \fI\&.\fP (saved mode).
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-b, \-\-browser <browser>
Browser to read cookies from.
.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Options
brave | chrome | chromium | edge | opera | vivaldi | firefox | safari
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-p, \-\-profile <profile>
Browser profile.
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-d, \-\-debug
Enable debug output.
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-q, \-\-quiet
Disable progress display updates.
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-S, \-\-sleep\-time <sleep_time>
Number of seconds yt\-dlp waits between requests.
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-no\-log
Ignore log (re\-fetch everything).
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-C, \-\-include\-comments
Also download all comments (extends download time significantly).
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-s, \-\-saved
Archive your saved posts instead of a profile (mutually exclusive with USERNAME).
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-u, \-\-unsave
Unsave posts after successful archive (only with \-\-saved).
.UNINDENT
.sp
Arguments
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B USERNAME
Optional argument
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
instagram\-archiver \-o ~/instagram\-backups/username username
instagram\-archiver \-\-saved \-o ~/instagram\-backups/saved
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
In profile mode the default output path is the username under the current working directory; in
\fB\-\-saved\fP mode it is the current working directory.
.sp
Videos are saved using yt\-dlp and its respective configuration.
